REACTION   ((5-B-10(N,A)3-LI-7,PAR,SIG)//
           (5-B-10(N,A)3-LI-7,PAR,SIG))
            the branching ratio defined as sig(n,a(0))/sig(n,a(1))
            given in the text as percent, but converted here into
            an absolute ratio.
CORRECTION  Corrected for epithermal neutrons. The measured
            reactor spectrum value was 6.741+-0.006%, and the
            epicadmium value was 7.02+-0.08%. With the measured
            cadmium ratio of the spectrum the value for epithermal
            neutrons and room background neutrons is given.
ERR-ANALYS (DATA-ERR) The uncertainty is one standard deviation,
            primarily from statistical counting uncertainties.
            The supplementary error from background was an order
            of magnitude smaller.
